<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/793851-currently-reading-and-just-started-book">Currently reading and just started book two in the series. Incredible!Wondering how others discovered the series - was it here? Also, there are gaps in time which are a bit disconcerting - wonder if anyone noticed that.</a>
</div>
