<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/85509163-shane"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1541267561i/85509163._UX100_CR0,30,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/85509163-shane">Shane</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">&quot;Lilith&apos;s Brood&quot; is the updated title of the trilogy that contains &quot;Dawn&quot;, &quot;Adulthood Rites&quot;, and &quot;Imago&quot;. The title of the trilogy was originally &quot;Xe<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">"Lilith's Brood" is the updated title of the trilogy that contains "Dawn", "Adulthood Rites", and "Imago". The title of the trilogy was originally "Xenogenesis".<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
